Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:07.29,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:34.69,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In search of the magic stone, Asta and the \Nothers arrived at the Underwater Temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:40.03,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,where they were forced to participate in High\NPriest Gifso's game, the Temple Battle Royale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:43.83,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,According to your ranking system,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:48.04,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,my temple mages would be more\Npowerful than intermediate knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:53.21,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:57.43,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I'm gonna get discouraged \Njust because I'm surrounded by water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:02.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Magna and Luck also participated in the game,\Nhoping to get the magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.35,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Ya snooze, ya lose, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.65,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Magic: Thunderbolt Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:17.32,main,Shark Mage,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, aren't you lively?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:21.82,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,My son is the strongest mage \Nof the Underwater Temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.82,0:01:23.43,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.70,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it... He's definitely \Nthe strongest one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:28.67,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,You two should come at me at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:31.92,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not hurt you \Nany more than I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:36.01,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea God's Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:38.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't ending anyone, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:40.99,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done having fun yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:48.45,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The one who appeared \Nbefore Magna and Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:51.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,was one of the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun's top brass, Vetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:55.07,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:59.57,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let us join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:32.81,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,480)}The Pointlessly Direct Fireball\Nand the Wild Lightning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:40.71,flashback,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a full moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:52.50,flashbackitalics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Asta is looking up \Nat the same moon right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:54.60,flashbackitalics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, silly me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:06.48,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha? I guess I fell asleep—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:10.82,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:24.38,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Not even good for a warm-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.59,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a pack of mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:28.88,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:29.68,flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.55,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:55.46,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I know we were all on vacation, but there \Nwere a number of senior Magic Knights here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:05:00.71,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,And they were all defeated by one guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:05.97,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,What were the Magic Knights we \Nbelieved in so much all about, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.29,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,That thing wasn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:11.10,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.50,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd this macho dude suddenly come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.86,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He looks pretty hardcore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:24.58,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, that shark guy was my prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:29.71,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is... This guy's magic \Npower is greater than Captain Yami's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.24,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,You made it through \Nthe rough ocean currents
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.91,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,and then forced your way in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:41.25,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,That's some incredible magic, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.13,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I guess you can still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.81,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:49.14,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure you're not a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.98,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you to the Underwater Temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:57.35,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,We're after the same thing as those \Ntwo over there, the magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:02.10,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But it's not like I'm \Njust going to hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:06.15,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't expect you to just hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:10.61,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to lay waste to everyone here,\Nmake you despair, and seize it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:11.86,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:15.58,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter and spread despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:16.69,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.32,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're all rather rude, abrupt guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.38,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Could you head on home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.88,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.30,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,That's also a pretty rude \Nway to address someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.17,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to get your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:33.93,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,do something about it,\Nand hit me with all your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:37.95,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're completely \Nunderestimating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:42.56,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look like it, but I am the \Nstrongest in the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:46.07,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Enough talk! Say it with your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.19,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:53.41,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea God's Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:04.35,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Magic: Rhinoceros Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.75,italics,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't even faze him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.48,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a bad spell, for a mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:15.76,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.10,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,A reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:21.27,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a reward called despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.68,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,This world is all about the \Nsurvival of the fittest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:27.86,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest beasts survive, and the \Nweak vermin live only to become prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:30.61,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Magic: Bear Claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:49.00,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a good feel for how \Nvastly different our powers are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:54.27,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You insects aren't even \Nallowed to hold on to hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:05.27,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:10.22,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,The temple's greatest warrior, Gio, \Nis being defeated so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:13.61,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:19.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, gramps. Playtime's over. \NHurry up and get me in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:25.25,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you insist... \NBut who in the world is this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:29.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the leaders of a nasty terror \Ngroup called the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.80,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:36.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to explain.\NWe're short on time, so hurry it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:39.27,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:42.93,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave here until the game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:47.94,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even undo the spell. \NThose are the rules of my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:49.65,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.61,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just let myself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:54.78,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:58.18,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Lightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:07.04,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:08.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.54,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:13.05,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic: Different Dimension Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.56,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're trapped in my spatial magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:20.80,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,no matter who you are,\Nyou won't be able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.56,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Black, foreign swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:28.14,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The mana tells me you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:31.19,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there and watch for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.73,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be my main dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:38.74,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,After I season you with despair, \Nas you watch all of your friends die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:43.78,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets out, the temple's done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:44.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:46.52,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.22,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it so they hear us out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:51.09,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.00,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.01,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Testing, testing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.80,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,That's the captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.72,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you dumbasses, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.59,top,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! I beat one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.97,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Someone really dangerous \Njust crashed the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.51,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the leaders of \Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:14.51,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and a beast of a man strong enough to go \Nhead-to-head with a Magic Knight Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.53,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:24.90,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Also, three of his underlings \Nare over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:26.65,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and hand over \Nthat yummy-looking food...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:29.84,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the problem... Due to reasons, \NI can't go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.33,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What do you mean, "reasons"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.58,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning you guys gotta \Ndo something about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.13,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:40.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, surpass your limits,\Nright here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.57,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:46.48,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.14,top,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:54.82,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought the game \Ncould get so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:59.65,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,It's a game that'll determine the fate \Nof the Underwater Temple, blast it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.24,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,The game rules have changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:04.41,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,No time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:09.91,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,To clear the game, defeat the\NEye of the Midnight Sun's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:12.26,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Those who contribute to clearing the game
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:18.07,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,will get any wish that's \Nwithin my power to grant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.42,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's an absolute monster here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:27.89,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:32.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That makes him worth fighting even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:36.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this... I'm gonna do this, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.32,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.11,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to put \Nour match on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Kiato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:48.66,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:53.38,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Who's my next prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.44,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:00.84,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could move on to the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:05.22,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We're still alive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:14.35,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,After what Mister Yami said, \NI can't just lie here napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.35,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.19,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.91,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...going to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.59,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:30.26,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The more stubborn the prey, the better \Nit is when they're finally in despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.19,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we managed to get back up,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:50.02,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,but how the hell are we supposed \Nto fight that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:53.38,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If he lands even one more decent \Nblow on us, we're finished... So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.56,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.02,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hit us with another one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:58.02,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:12:59.86,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That really fast one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.71,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Luck! What the hell?! Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:07.28,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We just barely managed to block that attack, \Nand we both still took a ton of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:11.53,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you're imitating me. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:14.16,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep giving you despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:16.19,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,until you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:28.30,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I thought! That spell leaves a \Nsplit-second opening right after you attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:31.68,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,So you're already matching my pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:34.89,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You've got good speed and sharp \Nsenses, I'll give you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:38.56,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My Thunderbolt Destruction \Ndidn't work at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.81,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play with you for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.61,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You speedy little...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:34.66,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That battle maniac... Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.66,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Magna, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:40.95,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.94,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luck. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:49.42,flashbackitalics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the guy who's called the Smiling\NCombat Fiend and Luck the Cheery Berserker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:52.68,flashbackitalics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I need to show him who's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:56.26,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, too, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:00.60,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.60,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a funny face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:06.98,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I joined the squad, he was an \Nannoying pest who messed with me constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.65,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,His personality was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.27,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,"This dude's got some serious issues."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.44,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot, hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:17.31,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.15,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:23.58,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Even on our missions,\Nhe would do insane things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:24.43,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.46,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.95,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Crackling Magna Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:47.04,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice but to admit that \Nhe has great battle instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:53.36,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And since that dungeon mission, \Nhe's gotten even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:58.53,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it,\Nbut you're my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:15:59.33,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.08,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:08.09,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare leave me behind, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:13.47,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Creation Magic: Grand Slam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:16.89,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna crush it over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:26.33,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.99,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:37.49,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you, I underestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:41.70,flashbackitalics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,A peasant, huh? He looks boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:45.46,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But my instincts warned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:50.75,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,They told me, "This guy's gonna \Nbe dangerous, yet interesting."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:54.51,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You interested me so much \Nthat I kept messing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.51,flashback,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That pudding you were \Nsaving sure was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:01.30,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to be your last supper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.52,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You always struck back at \Nme with everything you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:07.44,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I just now realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.77,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,that you're my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:12.24,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You're my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:18.79,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That you're my very first friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:22.49,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Magna! I bet you've got even more in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:25.00,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.43,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch, Fireball Gangster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.54,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a gangster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:38.84,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me, Lightning Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.64,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough playtime, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.86,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:46.14,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We're just about warmed up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:49.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:52.28,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell when you \Ncan't even sense mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:54.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sense mana, but I can sense ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:58.58,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Ki? It's true that I sense a \Nstrong magical power up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:01.19,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,And it's incredibly powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.70,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt anything like it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:07.45,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,But as you said, we've got to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:10.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your ki earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:14.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to sense your presence.\NHow were you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:20.97,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by dancing, I unconsciously \Nput myself into a trance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A trance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:26.17,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm in that state, my body moves \Nwithout me even having to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.98,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Then my opponents can't predict my movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:32.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So that's actually possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:32.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.79,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:39.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Putting myself into a trance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.91,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a clear view of that magic now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:46.49,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Flame and lightning magic are fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:50.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Flame and lightning... \NIt must be Magna and Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.71,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Their opponent has huge magic and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.33,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:58.17,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,It's like hundreds of raging beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:02.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Vetto! Wait, you can tell all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.47,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,My tribe's eyes are good at picking up magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.06,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,But if this is who we're up against...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:09.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:15.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are crazy, but when it comes \Ndown to it, they're both super reliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They definitely won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.57,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:26.93,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Do you finally get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:31.58,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The weak get eaten, and all \Nthey have left is despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:37.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Like we have time for that, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:38.80,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.34,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,If we were in despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:47.57,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be too embarrassed to \Nact like his superiors again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.10,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:03.99,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.74,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:12.12,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,that if we fight him normally,\Nwe probably won't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.83,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.17,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:25.25,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That slight opening we have \Nright after he attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:29.68,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:33.18,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hit him with all the magic we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:37.01,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,A simultaneous, full-power, body \Nand soul attack at close range?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:38.31,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they were trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:46.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Magna... Luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:47.78,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.28,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This power is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:56.79,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Combo Magic: Flame Lightning \NExplosive Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:05.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna! Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:50.49,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:49.43,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:53.99,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Crackling Magna Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:53.99,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Crackling Magna Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:56.38,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:59.58,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hear you! Put a little \Nmore umph into it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:04.79,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we're going to show you how you can \Ndo an easy Crackling Magna Typhoon at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.79,0:23:07.64,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,First, have a string of lightning ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:08.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,No one can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.46,0:23:11.66,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you wrap that lightning \Nstring around Magna, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:12.98,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It's electrocuting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:15.11,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you'll have to get your own Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:16.47,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,They can't do that, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:18.69,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Once you wrap the lightning \Nstring around him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:21.39,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to spin him with \Nall your strength like a top.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:23.41,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:25.86,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the Crackling Magna Typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:26.76,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:29.51,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can do this, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:33.15,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:33.15,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:37.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never give up, no matter \Nhow powerful my enemy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:42.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I'm... We're the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:46.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 45: " The Guy \NWho Doesn't Know When to Quit."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:50.39,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 45\N\N{\fs18} The Guy Who Doesn't Know When to Quit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:47.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:49.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic!
